Package: options
Type: Package
Title: Lightweight and Powerful Option Manager for R
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2014-10-22
Author: Mark van der Loo
Maintainer: Mark vand er Loo <mark.vanderloo@gmail.com>
Description: Easily define option sets, and add/remove or reset options to
    defaults. This option manager is somewhat similar to futile.options, except
    that it allows to clone and merge options making it easy to implement local
    vs global options, possibly in a multilevel option hierarchy. See the
    package vignette for examples.
URL: https://github.com/markvanderloo/options
License: GPL-3
VignetteBuilder: knitr
Suggests:
    testthat,
    knitr
